INSTALLATION
    Ondine can be easily compiled and installed. See file "INSTALL" for
    instructions. Please also have a look at the file "REQUIREMENTS" for
    information on the tools required to run, compile, and develop Anastasia.


DOCUMENTATION
    The directory "doc" contains a documentation of Ondine. It can also be
    downloaded at <http://service-technology.org/files/ondine/ondine.pdf>.
